<br>
I agree on the HP rings. Have a set of velium diamond rings for raids, your MR is too low. About 600p-1kp each.<br>
<br>
Try to get your STA over 100. To that end, work on your range slot. Maybe add a velium (or platinum) bloodstone earring to bump sta over 100.<br>
<br>
Range slot:<br>
<br>
Start camping in Chardok. Some nice items drop there: <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6836">Sarnak War bow</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (no drop, +5 sta), or <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6809">Bronze statue of Bathezid</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (+6 sta, droppable but will cost a fortune)<br>
<br>
Or...maybe find a potter to make you a Karana idol, if you are not interested in camping an <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=4023">idol of the thorned</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (+10 sta, costs over 10k and is very rough to solo at your level, plan on MR &gt;90 to do it).<br>
<br>
Magic Resist:<br>
Head back to Mistmoore for a crested Mistmoore shield (400-600p), or if you got lucky in Chardok, a Sarnak Battleshield (better and adds STA, but sells for 5k on my server).<br>
<br>
Plane of air:<br>
Shop for new stuff there. A really really nice <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=993">pally haste belt</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> is quested there. Oh look, Firey Avenger parts are done there too. Guess you are headed there anyway....<br>
<br>
If you *do* manage to obtain the Girdle of Faith (now that the ivory sky diamonds are back in the game), sell your FBSS for some blue diamond earrings, if you are lucky, you might get a pair of them.<br>
